{
  "text": "MRI scans were performed on a 1 T Siemens Magnetom Impact (Siemens Healthcare, Frimley, UK). Staging scans were carried out as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Dynamic scans used a sagittal 2D T 1 -weighted FLASH sequence (TR/TE \u00bc 130/6.5 ms, FOV \u00bc 290 \u00c2 290 \u00c2 5 mm, matrix \u00bc 256 \u00c2 256, NSA \u00bc 1, a \u00bc 701) with a temporal resolution of 25 s. One sequence of nine contiguous slices covering the whole-tumour volume was obtained before and seven after injection of 0.1 mmol kg \u00c01 body weight Gd-DTPA.",
